data.description: SELLER CONCESSIONS OF $5,000!!! This charming and also spacious single level rambler home has been updated throughout. Located on a quiet street with easy access to the free way and walking distance to town. You will fall in love with the big open kitchen with a large island, the 2 living rooms, big bedrooms, ample storage and fully fenced in backyard. Cozy up on the couch while enjoying the ambiance of the efficient pellet stoves on each floor. You really don't want to miss the opportunity to snag this one up and start the New Year in a new home.
